OL,5, Supermarket Morrisons has confirmed it 
OL,6, has cut sick pay for unvaccinated      
OL,7, workers who are forced to isolate after
OL,8, being exposed to Covid.                
OL,10,FIt follows similar moves from big      
OL,11,Fretailers including Ikea, Next and     
OL,12,FOcado as staff absences rise.          
OL,14,FUnjabbed Morrisons workers who are told
OL,15,Fto isolate but test negative now get   
OL,16,Fstatutory sick pay of #96.35 a week.   
OL,18,FCovid-positive staff get full sick pay 
OL,19,Fregardless of vaccination status. The  
OL,20,Ffirm pays staff at least #10 per hour. 
